íŸ@f44fa4a66c903fcd83a6d5813645360912a05ed2d2ec7396cc1b3e0906592c9e⁄–Title: title: random float
Path: Examples
Content:
Generate a default float value between 0 and 1.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random float


```
Generate a random float less than or equal to 500.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random float ..500


```
Generate a random float greater than or equal to 100000.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random float 100000..


```
Generate a random float between 1.0 and 1.1.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random float 1.0..1.1


```
